- cs.GR: The paper discusses the simulation of an urban environment using SimCity 1's game engine, which involves graphics and visualization, falling under the sub-category of computer graphics. 
- cs.SY: The paper mentions the interactive nature of the environment, which involves human interaction and control, falling under the sub-category of systems and control.
